                            <comment id="98520" author="bogl" created="Thu, 6 Nov 2014 15:41:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;POR for master is changing. The new plan is to continue being able to build on el6.5 while enabling build on el6.6.  This is a departure from previous common practice.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
